---
// src/components/FAQ.astro
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/20" id="faq">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-16 tracking-tight">
            Common Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <details
                class="group bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-neutral-800 open:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-8 cursor-pointer list-none"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >How much does it cost?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-rounded text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 text-3xl"
                        >add</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="px-8 pb-8 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed"
                >
                    We have 0 onboarding fees. You can create and launch your
                    Panchasara store for free and start selling immediately.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-neutral-800 open:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-8 cursor-pointer list-none"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >Do I need technical skills?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-rounded text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 text-3xl"
                        >add</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="px-8 pb-8 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed"
                >
                    No technical skills needed. If you can upload a photo to
                    Instagram, you can build a Panchasara store. Your store can
                    be set up and live in about 5 minutes.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-neutral-800 open:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-8 cursor-pointer list-none"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >How do I share my store with customers?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-rounded text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 text-3xl"
                        >add</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="px-8 pb-8 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Once your store is live, you’ll get a store link . You can
                    share it in your Instagram bio, WhatsApp, or send it
                    directly through DMs so customers can order easily.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-neutral-800 open:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-8 cursor-pointer list-none"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >What can I sell on Panchasara?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-rounded text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 text-3xl"
                        >add</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="px-8 pb-8 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Panchasara is perfect for home bakers, small food
                    businesses, and handmade product sellers who want a simple
                    online store without the hassle of building a website.
                </div>
            </details>

            <details
                class="group bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-neutral-800 open:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex justify-between items-center w-full p-8 cursor-pointer list-none"
                >
                    <span
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >Do I need to build a website separately?</span
                    >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-rounded text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300 text-3xl"
                        >add</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="px-8 pb-8 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed"
                >
                    No. Your Panchasara store acts as your website, so customers
                    can browse products, see details, and place orders all in
                    one place.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
